At that time there was far less standardization with hardware.

21
00:01:06.829 --> 00:01:09.280
It's good that we don't have to do that nowadays.

22
00:01:09.280 --> 00:01:14.191
The installation of Windows 10 is just crazy easy how streamlined it is.

23
00:01:14.191 --> 00:01:16.892
Now how does this installation work in the real world.

24
00:01:16.892 --> 00:01:20.458
Most consumers I dare say never have to do an installation

25
00:01:20.458 --> 00:01:23.122
or a reinstallation because their OEM,

26
00:01:23.122 --> 00:01:25.876
their original equipment manufacturer has already

